In the Matter of Nicholas MORANO, Appellant. Tony Burnoski, Appellee. No. 25. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Oct. 15, 1934. Arthur L. Burchell, of Brooklyn, N. Y., for bankrupt. Michaels & Michaels, of New York City (William A. Michaels, of New York City, of counsel), for creditor appellee.

Before MANTON, L. HAND, and SWAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed.
